/// `system.collections.transformable` — compatibility shim.
///
/// The `Transformable<T>`, `Foldable<T>`, and `Sequenced<T>` traits now live in
/// `system.collections.list` so their default method bodies can construct a
/// `List<T>` without forming a stdlib import cycle.
///
/// Importing this module forwards to `system.collections.list` so existing
/// `use system.collections.transformable` statements continue to work.

use system.collections.list
